videos.description: Boston College RB Jon Hilliman takes the toss and lowers his shoulder on his way into the end zone to open up the scoring against Maryland.
videos.headline: Hilliman powers through defender for Boston College TD

videos.description: Boston College quarterback Patrick Towles rolls to his right and then throws to a wide open Tommy Sweeney in the end zone for a 2-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: BC's Sweeney wide open for 2-yard TD

videos.description: Perry Hills sacked by Kevin Kavalec for a loss of 8 yards to the Mary 10 Perry Hills fumbled, forced by Kevin Kavalec, recovered by BC Truman Gutapfel , return for 0 yards , return for 7 yds to the Mary 10
videos.headline: P. Hills strip sacked by K. Kavalec recovered by BC T. Gutapfel

videos.description: Maryland running back Ty Johnson bursts through the line of scrimmage and runs past multiple Boston College defenders en route to a 62-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Maryland's Johnson speeds 62 yards for a touchdown

videos.description: Boston College runs a tricky play with wide receiver Jeff Smith throwing to a wide open quarterback Patrick Towles for a 20-yard touchdown in the second quarter against Maryland.
videos.headline: BC gets tricky on 20-yard touchdown in bowl win

videos.description: Maryland's Ty Johnson finds a crease for a 30-yard touchdown, his second of the quarter. The Terrapins try to complete a jump pass on the two-point conversion, but it is no good.
videos.headline: Maryland's Johnson scores 30-yard TD, Terps fail 2-point conversion

videos.description: Boston College's Harold Landry reaches out and snags Perry Hills' pass for an interception.
videos.headline: Boston College DE makes great interception

videos.description: Halftime interview with Boston College head coach Steve Addazio, looking to come out with "more energy"
videos.headline: Halftime interview with Boston College head coach Steve Addazio, looking to come out with "more energy"

videos.description: Boston College QB Patrick Towles finds Michael Walker along the sidelines for a 49-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Boston College extends lead with 49-yard touchdown

videos.description: After scoring a touchdown, Maryland attempts a two-point conversion with running back Kenneth Goins Jr. taking the snap, but he overthrows tight end Avery Edwards.

videos.headline: Maryland can't duplicate the Dontari Poe jump pass

videos.description: With Maryland deep in their own end, Ty Johnson gets the handoff but is hit hard by Boston College's Noa Merritt. The ball bounces backwards and recovered by Kevin Kavalec for defensive touchdown for the Eagles.
videos.headline: BC recovers fumble for defensive TD

videos.description: Maryland's Teldrick Mogan goes deep and catches the pass, then runs away from a hobbled Boston College defender to score a 63-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Maryland's Morgan gets easy 63-yard touchdown

videos.description: Maryland's Levern Jacobs makes a nice adjustment to grab the ball then get away from two Boston College defenders to score a 52-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Maryland's Jacobs grabs, runs past BC defense for 52-yard score
